{"tid":1702293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我今晚要屌撚死班狗佢","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T16:58:14.000Z","uid":39356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae24e37647f6e4c0fff9e1ed376a7046ffdac248","tid":1702293,"uid":39356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌閪咩 醒下啦 </span><br />\n屌狗個成本同效益成正比咩？<br />\n成日有人因為近距離屌狗而比人拉 <br />\n你地唔撚會覺得好撚無謂？<br />\n<br />\n根本係人都知會濫捕 你仲挑釁佢地<br />\n比人拉撚咗就扮無辜 以為人地會可憐你<br />\n<br />\n真係訓撚醒未啊？要可憐我地一早可憐咗啦<br />\n抗爭緊啊 仲小朋友𦧲地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真係唔撚該大家 真係為場運動著想嘅<br />\n咪撚貪一時口爽啦<br />\n收一收把口 留命做其他嘢</span><br />\n<br />\n真係要屌狗都唔該企到遠一遠<br />\n咪撚on99兜口兜面屌 冇人救撚到你<br />\n亦唔撚會覺得你有幾撚型<br />\n只係覺得你有勇無謀on99"},{"pid":"1d4e2fb1e4d6ab3c7dfb8b7e9aeedf2c4b6a6426","tid":1702293,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"凌晨荃灣凌晨荃灣凌晨荃灣凌晨荃灣"},{"pid":"60f68006cb195a0723c4cec022a96d53116cc30c","tid":1702293,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45wpEqc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45wpEqc.png&h=efd0aff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oamGHe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oamGHe.jpg&h=e374f630&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}